{"type": "article", "id": 14282, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。\r\n", "date": "2015-09-02T08:27:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 767, "name": "家具设计"}, {"id": 15319, "name": "IISE"}, {"id": 15320, "name": "specialized"}, {"id": 15321, "name": "Sovrappensiero"}, {"id": 15322, "name": "Raul Frollà"}, {"id": 15323, "name": "Robert Egger"}, {"id": 15324, "name": "Charbel Gharibeh"}, {"id": 15325, "name": "Stephanie Sayar"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607163627IuAikPE8yTxbG6Hw.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t</p>\n<h3>\r\n\t\tRoll Vertical Scroll Calendar by Sovrappensiero Design Studio\r\n\t</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这个像软尺的装置其实是一个无限循环的日历，左边是星期数，右边是日期，最上方的红色标杆指向了今天，暗示了时间的无限循环。日历套在木质的滚轮上，可以安在墙上查看。有绿、蓝、灰三种颜色选择，统一售价 67.29 美元。<a href=\"http://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/roll-vertical-scroll-calendar/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163612x7j3YbsD6hyGIzR2.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071636128S0gLpJKz5CoIeOx.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163613YJ9Iv4yHVapODTRG.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.92340426\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163613PD1WRl9Ts4JXOyIp.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t</p>\n<h3>\r\n\t\tTHE LOVERS’ STOOL by Charbel Gharibeh &amp; Stephanie Sayar \r\n\t</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这把方凳是可以滑开的，也可以当咖啡桌。它的侧边源于阿拉伯国家黎巴嫩的拱形建筑，拉开方凳，侧面依然维持了优雅的弧度。用木材制作而没有任何别的装饰，突出了它的结构。设计师是出生于黎巴嫩的年轻夫妇，他们想要以此提醒人们对老建筑的关注。<a href=\"http://www.squad-design.com/pages/stools%20exhibition/charbel_and_stephanie_arcus.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163614mT7u6f5DjkxKLGEv.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.57222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071636142qGJaOhkusxWY4lC.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.57166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163615ckrwnEqVWgfKOJvb.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.57333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163615beSX3UNYoGKmORxs.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.57166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163615iM3f7PgLSG12J8C0.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.57166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163616CeHhGfSAq135F7Ld.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t</p>\n<h3>\r\n\t\tMoai Terracotta Vase by Raul Frollà<span></span> \r\n\t</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这两个花瓶来自意大利的设计师 Raul Frollà，灵感来源于复活岛上的石像，两侧的把手模拟了人像的两只耳朵，的确有单纯静穆的力量。瓶身没有任何装饰，采用浅灰或天蓝两种纯色，非常光洁干净，以反衬出花朵的鲜艳。这组花瓶有高矮两种型号，分别售价 104.3 美元和 98.69 美元。<a href=\"http://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/moai-terracotta-vase/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163617BrqbchEzKaZQlRTd.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.90425532\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163617aNp8H3X2vEgmPJOM.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.48617021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163617OXRmSVLZ3ePw9yfn.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.84468085\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163618jbFGzvVQ5guMs0Sd.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t</p>\n<h3>\r\n\t\tIISE by Jas\r\n\t</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t韩国手工艺包饰品牌 IISE 在韩语里是“第二代”。今年的秋冬系列，推出 Daypack 、Tech 和 Slimpack 三种不同型号的黑色双肩背包。选用上等牛皮、帆布和植物鞣山羊皮等材料，简单时尚。不得不说，这种黑色皮质的双肩包是经典百搭款。<a href=\"http://store.hypebeast.com/cn/brands/iise?utm_source=Hypebeast.cc&amp;utm_campaign=IISE%202015%20Fall%2FWinter%20Backpacks%20Collection&amp;utm_medium=Editorial%20Post%20Buy%20Now%20Button\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071636186LrdFjl8J1V9HMvB.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163619HzbhnGqExof9cKYp.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163620CGJWgj52AX3iKkZ8.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071636201HCn47ukP0hfKDVL.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163621yO4S7Cm2lXT0Vgpq.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t</p>\n<h3>\r\n\t\t可弯折的创可贴 by Lin Huahui\r\n\t</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t普通的创可贴一旦贴在手指关节处，就难以弯曲手指，十分僵硬，很多时候没等伤口痊愈就把创可贴撕掉了。如果能将贴纸的中间掏空，使弯曲部位露出来，其实就能解决这个问题。简单的设计，你没想到吧。<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2015/09/01/bendy-wendy-bandaid/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163621Pdi2aDJtwIO0mvbp.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.73333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163622yuU3pZtSMwVIqiHh.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.28761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163622f4His3yoKeNqpWmO.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.42190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163623Gh3KLUClyZpTwFzd.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.48666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163623w7mM3pkB0W1PYuDO.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.48571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t</p>\n<h3>\r\n\t\tfUCI by Robert Egger\r\n\t</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这款非常酷炫的自行车来自specialized 的创始人 Robert Egger，他想要突破 UCI（国际自行车联盟）对自行车的诸多规定。采用空气流线型的车体，模拟了鸟的头部以减小阻力，而 33.3 英寸的超大后轮，也能大幅度提高车速。同时，在自行车里安装可采用太阳能充电的锂电池，启动时只需要按动马达，就能轻松上路。头部的空位留给了智能手机，座椅还可以存放物品，与市场上的设计非常不一样。Robert Egger 将它命名为“ eff you see eye ”即“ fUCI ”，但目前还只是一个概念。<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/technology/specialized-fuci-bike-concept-robert-egger-08-31-2015/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163624zFLOsh83qWf1CjTp.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.80317848\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071636249exagYLjkT5yzidK.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163625A3l1Rn0MLx8QX5ra.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163625ApO8zHqtJsveLVXi.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163626UefdE7upcDwH5IkL.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607163626AczxT1vIMX27as5w.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}